#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kuidas mängida"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Eesmärk:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Put the ball into the hole with the least possible hits."
msgstr "lüüa pall auku võimalikult väheste löökidega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname;'s game-play is simple. It is the easiest to learn how to play "
#| "hands-on, and thus a tutorial course is included to guide you through the "
#| "basics. This chapter will guide you through this tutorial. To start the "
#| "tutorial, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Tutorial</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"&kolf;'s game-play is simple. It is the easiest to learn how to play hands-"
"on, and thus a tutorial course is included to guide you through the basics. "
"This chapter will guide you through this tutorial. To start the tutorial, "
"choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tutorial</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"&kappname;i mängimine on tegelikult ääretult lihtne. Treening pakub "
"võimalust õppida golfi mängima ning seetõttu juhib see väljak sind läbi "
"erinevate elementide, õpetades selgeks põhitõed. See peatükk kirjeldabki "
"treeningut. Treeningu käivitamiseks mängus vali <menuchoice><guimenu>Abi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Treening</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hitting the Ball"
msgstr "Palli löömine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To aim the ball, either line up the mouse behind the ball so the putter "
#| "aims in the direction you want to hit it or press one of the <keycap>Left "
#| "Arrow</keycap> (counterclockwise) or <keycap>Right Arrow</keycap> "
#| "(clockwise) keys, to rotate the putter."
msgid ""
"To aim the ball, either line up the mouse behind the ball so the putter aims "
"in the direction you want to hit it or press one of the &Left; arrow "
"(counterclockwise) or &Right; arrow (clockwise) keys, to rotate the putter."
msgstr ""
"Palli löömiseks aseta hiir palli taha, nii et golfikepp ehk putter osutaks "
"suunas, kuhu soovid lüüa, või vajuta kas klahvi <keycap>Nool vasakule</"
"keycap> (vastupäeva) või <keycap>Nool paremale</keycap> (päripäeva) putteri "
"keeramiseks vajalikku suunda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To rotate the putter more quickly with the keyboard, hold down &Shift; while "
"pressing or holding the arrow keys. To rotate more slowly, hold down &Ctrl;."
msgstr ""
"Putteri kiiremaks keeramiseks klaviatuuri abil hoia nooleklahvile vajutades "
"all klahvi &Shift;. Aeglasemaks keeramiseks aga vajuta klahvi &Ctrl;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To hit the ball, press and hold either the &LMB; or <keycap>Down Arrow</"
#| "keycap> key. The longer you hold down the key or button, the more "
#| "strength the putt will have. It will take practice to get a good feel for "
#| "speed."
msgid ""
"To hit the ball, press and hold either the &LMB; or &Down; arrow key. The "
"longer you hold down the key or button, the more strength the putt will "
"have. It will take practice to get a good feel for speed."
msgstr ""
"Palli löömiseks vajuta ja hoia all &HVN; või klahv <keycap>Nool alla</"
"keycap>. Mida kauem nuppu või klahvi all hoiad, seda tugevam löök tuleb. "
"Õige löögitugevuse tunde kättesaamiseks võib kuluda päris hulk aega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To stop the putt while you are still holding moving the putter back in your "
"stroke, press &Esc;."
msgstr ""
"Löögi peatamiseks pärast seda, kui oled juba hakanud putterit liigutama, "
"vajuta klahvi &Esc;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hit the ball into the hole to move on to the next."
msgstr "Järgmisele rajale pääsemiseks löö pall auku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:90 index.docbook:682
#, no-c-format
msgid "Slopes"
msgstr "Kallakud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Slopes are slanted areas of the course that the golf ball rolls down in "
#| "an expected manner. The light of the golf course is from the upper-left, "
#| "so the brightest slopes will push the ball towards the upper-left corner "
#| "of the hole. Choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show "
#| "Info</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to see an arrow that points in the "
#| "direction the slope will roll the ball."
msgid ""
"Slopes are slanted areas of the course that the golf ball rolls down in an "
"expected manner. The light of the golf course is from the upper-left, so the "
"brightest slopes will push the ball towards the upper-left corner of the "
"hole. Choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Info</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to see an arrow that points in the "
"direction the slope will roll the ball."
msgstr ""
"Kallakud on alad, mida mööda golfipall veereb alla teatud kindlal viisil. "
"Golfiväljaku valgustus tuleb ülalt vasakult, nii et heledamad kallakud "
"suunavad palli järelikult ülespoole ja vasakule. Kui soovid näha, millises "
"suunas kallakud palli suunavad, vali vastavaid nooli esile toov menüükäsk "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Rada</guimenu><guimenuitem>Näita infot</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this tutorial hole, hit the ball onto the upward-pointing slope and let "
"it roll into the cup to move onto the next hole."
msgstr ""
"Sellel õpperajal löö järgmisele rajale pääsemiseks pall mööda kallakut üles "
"ja lase tal auku veereda."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Directions"
msgstr "Suunad"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "On the next hole, experiment with the other kinds of slopes. There are "
#| "elliptical, vertical, horizontal, and diagonal slopes in &kappname;. Hit "
#| "the ball into the hole."
msgid ""
"On the next hole, experiment with the other kinds of slopes. There are "
"elliptical, vertical, horizontal, and diagonal slopes in &kolf;. Hit the "
"ball into the hole."
msgstr ""
"Järgmisel rajal saad harjutada erinevate kallakutüüpidega. &kappname; pakub "
"ringjaid, vertikaalseid, horisontaalseid ja diagonaalseid kallakuid."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Steepness"
msgstr "Kalle"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The next tutorial hole has two slopes of differing steepness. If you "
#| "choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Info</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice>, the steepness of the slope will appear as a "
#| "number from 1-8, where 8 is steepest and 1 is shallowest. Hit the ball "
#| "into the hole and continue to the next hole."
msgid ""
"The next tutorial hole has two slopes of differing steepness. If you choose "
"the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Info</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item, the steepness of the slope will appear "
"as a number from 1-8, where 8 is steepest and 1 is shallowest. Hit the ball "
"into the hole and continue to the next hole."
msgstr ""
"Järgmisel rajal on kaks erineva kaldega kallakut. Kui valid "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Rada</guimenu><guimenuitem>Näita infot</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, näed kalde suurust numbrina vahemikus 1 kuni 8, kus 8 on kõige "
"järsem ja 1 kõige laugem. Löö pall auku ja asu järgmise raja kallale."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Walls"
msgstr "Seinad"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Balls bounce of walls as one would expect them to, with a little bit of "
"dampening. Deflect the ball off the walls and into the cup to advance to the "
"next hole."
msgstr ""
"Pallid põrkavad seintelt tagasi, nagu võibki oodata, ühtlasi aeglustab sein "
"natuke nende hoogu ja võib ka muuta suunda, kui on löödud nurga all. "
"Järgmisele rajale pääsemiseks löö pall põrkega seina vastu auku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:107 index.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid "Puddles and Sand"
msgstr "Lombid ja liiv"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Puddles"
msgstr "Lombid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Puddles are blue. When your ball rolls into a puddle, a penalty stroke is "
"added to your score and you must then choose where you want to take your "
"next shot from: either next to the puddle or from the same place as where "
"you just took the last shot."
msgstr ""
"Lombid on sinised. Kui pall satub lompi, lisatakse karistuslöök ning sa pead "
"valima, kus soovid ette võtta järgise löögi: kas otse lombi kõrval või samas "
"kohas, kus sooritasid viimase löögi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sand"
msgstr "Liiv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sand is yellow. Balls roll through sand very slowly."
msgstr "Liiv on kollane. Pallid liiguvad liival väga aeglaselt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hit the ball around the puddles and through the sand into the hole to "
"continue to the next tutorial hole."
msgstr ""
"Järgmisele rajale pääsemiseks löö pall ümber lompide ja üle liiva auku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:117 index.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid "Windmills"
msgstr "Tuuleveskid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Windmills are compound objects with brown border walls and a moving arm on "
"one side. Half-walls create the opening to the windmill, which the black arm "
"swings across. It takes practice to be able to time the stroke of the ball "
"to pass through the opening. Hit the ball through the windmill into the hole "
"to continue."
msgstr ""
"Tuuleveskid on keerukamad objektid pruunide seinte ning liikuva tiivikuga "
"ühel küljel. Poolseinad tekitavad tuuleveskisse avause, mille ees tiivik "
"liigub. Nõuab natuke harjutamist, enne kui suudad ajastada löögi täpselt "
"läbima avaust - kuid ainult nii pääseb edasi järgmisele rajale."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Black Holes"
msgstr "Mustad augud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When you hit your ball into a black hole, it is transported to the exit "
#| "and ejected at the angle of the exit at a speed directly relational to "
#| "the speed your ball was going. Choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Info</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to see which "
#| "Black Hole goes to which exit and which direction the ball will come out "
#| "of the exit. The rim around Black Holes are the same color as their "
#| "corresponding exits. Hit the ball into the black hole, which will then "
#| "eject the ball into the cup so you can go to the next hole."
msgid ""
"When you hit your ball into a black hole, it is transported to the exit and "
"ejected at the angle of the exit at a speed directly relational to the speed "
"your ball was going. Choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show Info</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to see which "
"Black Hole goes to which exit and which direction the ball will come out of "
"the exit. The rim around Black Holes are the same color as their "
"corresponding exits. Hit the ball into the black hole, which will then eject "
"the ball into the cup so you can go to the next hole."
msgstr ""
"Kui lööd palli musta auku, toimetatakse see musta augu väljapääsu juurde ja "
"paisatakse sealt välja teatud nurga all kiirusega, mis on seotud palli musta "
"auku viinud löögi kiirusega. Vali <menuchoice><guimenu>Rada</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Näita infot</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, kui soovid "
"näha, millisest väljapääsust ja mis suunas pall mustast august väljub. Musta "
"augu ja tema väljapääsu servad on ühesugust värvi. Löö pall musta auku, kust "
"see saab lennata auku, et pääseda järgmisele rajale."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:125 index.docbook:749
#, no-c-format
msgid "Floaters"
msgstr "Hõljukid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Floaters are moving platforms that carry a ball that lands on it. Floaters' "
"speeds vary. This one is a pretty slow floater, but you still must time your "
"shot so you can go over the wall and into the cup."
msgstr ""
"Hõljukid on liikuvad alused, mis kannavad endale sattunud palli. Nende "
"liikumiskiirus on rajati erinev. Treeningrajal on tegemist üsna aeglase "
"hõljukiga, kuid siiski tuleb sul oma löök täpselt ajastada, et hõljuk saaks "
"toimetada palli üle seina auguni."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bridges"
msgstr "Sillad"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bridges are simple - they just lift the ball above the things below them, "
"like slopes, sand, and puddles. They can have brown walls on their perimeter."
msgstr ""
"Sillad on väga lihtsad objektid - nad lihtsalt võimaldavad pallil veereda "
"üle selle, mis silla alla jääb, olgu selleks siis kallak, liiv või lomp. "
"Sillad võivad mõnest küljest olla piiratud seinaga."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Mängureeglid, strateegia ja nõuanded"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Here's in-depth description of &kappname;'s basic features."
msgid "Here's in-depth description of &kolf;'s basic features."
msgstr "Allpool on esitatud &kappname;i põhiomaduste põhjalik kirjeldus."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting a Game"
msgstr "Mängu käivitamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To start a game, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This opens a dialog "
#| "where you can configure your new game."
msgid ""
"To start a game, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. This opens a dialog "
"where you can configure your new game."
msgstr ""
"Mängu käivitamiseks vali <menuchoice><guimenu>Mäng</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Uus</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. See avab dialoogi, kus "
"saab uut mängu seadistada."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Players Page"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a player to your game, click the <guibutton>New Player</guibutton> "
"button."
msgstr "Mängija lisamiseks klõpsa nupule <guibutton>Uus mängija</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "To change the name of the players, change the text in the text boxes."
msgstr "Mängijate nime muutmiseks muuda teksti tekstikastides."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove a player, click the <guibutton>Remove</guibutton> button next to "
"the player's name."
msgstr "Mängija eemaldamiseks klõpsa nupule <guibutton>Eemalda</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:167
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Course name:"
msgid "Course Page"
msgstr "Väljaku nimi:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To choose the course that you want to play, click its entry in the list "
#| "box on the left of this page. &kappname; comes with many built-in courses "
#| "that you can play."
msgid ""
"To choose the course that you want to play, click its entry in the list box "
"on the left of this page. &kolf; comes with many built-in courses that you "
"can play."
msgstr ""
"Soovitava väljaku valimiseks klõpsa selle kirjel kaardi vasakus servas "
"asuvas nimekirjakastis. &kappname; pakub mitmeid erinevaid väljakuid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To add a course that you have downloaded or made, click on the "
#| "<guibutton>Add...</guibutton> button on the bottom of this page, and "
#| "choose the course file in the file dialog."
msgid ""
"To add a course that you have downloaded or made, click on the "
"<guibutton>Add…</guibutton> button on the bottom of this page, and choose "
"the course file in the file dialog."
msgstr ""
"Veebist tõmmatud või omaloodud väljaku lisamiseks klõpsa nupule "
"<guibutton>Lisa...</guibutton> ning vali ilmuvas failidialoogis soovitud "
"väljakufail."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options Page"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this page you can choose whether or not this game will be played in "
"<guilabel>Strict mode</guilabel>. In strict mode, there is no undo, moving "
"holes, or editing of the course. This mode is generally for competition. "
"Only in strict mode are high scores kept."
msgstr ""
"Sellel kaardil saad valida, kas mängu mängitakse <guilabel>Ranges režiimis</"
"guilabel> või mitte. Range režiimi korral ei saa lööke tagasi võtta, radu "
"vahetada ega väljakut redigeerida. Üldiselt on see režiim mõeldud "
"võistlemiseks. Ka rekordeid salvestatakse ainult range režiimi korral."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saved Games"
msgstr "Salvestatud mängud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; can keep a history of your rounds that are still in progress "
#| "and save them to disk so you can load them and play them later. Saved "
#| "games include the current hole, names and colors of all players in game, "
#| "and the scores of the players."
msgid ""
"&kolf; can keep a history of your rounds that are still in progress and save "
"them to disk so you can load them and play them later. Saved games include "
"the current hole, names and colors of all players in game, and the scores of "
"the players."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; peab meeles sinu läbitud radu ning võib need kettale salvestada, "
"et sa saaksid soovi korral mängu hiljem jätkata. Salvestatud mängud jätavad "
"meelde poolelijäänud raja, kõigi mängijate nimed ja värvid, samuti iga "
"mängija skoori."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving Your Game"
msgstr "Mängu salvestamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To save your game while still playing, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Game</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. If you have "
#| "not saved a game on this game before, you will be prompted for the file "
#| "to save to."
msgid ""
"To save your game while still playing, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Game</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. If you "
"have not saved a game on this game before, you will be prompted for the file "
"to save to."
msgstr ""
"Mängu salvestamiseks mängimise ajal vali <menuchoice><guimenu>Mäng</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Salvesta mäng</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Kui sa ei "
"ole antud mängu varem salvestanud, palutakse sul sisestada failinimi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loading Your Game"
msgstr "Mängu avamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To load the game that you saved, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Load...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. You can then "
#| "choose the saved game to open."
msgid ""
"To load the game that you saved, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Load…</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item. You can "
"then choose the saved game to open."
msgstr ""
"Salvestatud mängu taaslaadimiseks vali <menuchoice><guimenu>Mäng</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Ava...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, misjärel saad "
"valida, millise mängu soovid avada."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "Practicing"
msgstr "Harjutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are a few features that make practicing your golf easier. These "
"features are not enabled during strict mode."
msgstr ""
"Mitu lisavõimalust muudavad golfi mängimise hõlpsamaks. Range režiimi korral "
"ei ole need võimalused lubatud."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Undo"
msgstr "Tagasivõtmine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To undo a bad shot, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Undo Shot</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"To undo a bad shot, choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Hole</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Undo Shot</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Kehva löögi tagasivõtmiseks vali <menuchoice><guimenu>Rada</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Võta löök tagasi</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switching Holes"
msgstr "Radade vahetamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>Go</guimenu> menu contains many menu items for switching to "
"different holes that are quite self explanatory. See the <link linkend=\"go-"
"menu\"><guimenu>Go</guimenu> menu reference</link>."
msgstr ""
"Menüü <guimenu>Liikumine</guimenu> võimaldab mitut moodi suunduda "
"käesolevalt mõnele muule rajale, nende nimetused peaksid ise enda eest "
"kõnelema. Vaata lähemalt <link linkend=\"go-menu\">menüü <guimenu>Liikumine</"
"guimenu> käskude seletusi</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Putting Options"
msgstr "Puttamisvõimalused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; has a few ways to putt. The basic putting method is <link "
#| "linkend=\"hitting\">described above</link>."
msgid ""
"&kolf; has a few ways to putt. The basic putting method is <link linkend="
"\"hitting\">described above</link>."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; pakub puttamiseks mitu võimalust. Põhimeetodit sai kirjeldatud "
"juba <link linkend=\"hitting\">eespool</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The mouse is enabled by default. This means that whenever the mouse is "
"moved, the putter aligns to the line between the mouse and ball."
msgstr ""
"Vaikimisi on hiire kasutamine lubatud. See tähendab, et kui sa hiirt "
"liigutad, võtab putter sisse asendi hiirekursori ja palli vahel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you prefer to only use the keyboard and arrow keys, you can disable "
#| "mouse putting by unchecking <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Enable Mouse for Moving Putter</guimenuitem></"
#| "menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"If you prefer to only use the keyboard and arrow keys, you can disable mouse "
"putting by unchecking the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Enable Mouse for Moving Putter</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Kui eelistad kasutada ainult klaviatuuri ja nooleklahve, saad hiire "
"kasutamise keelata, eemaldades märke menüükäsu "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu><guimenuitem>Putteri liigutamine "
"hiirega lubatud</guimenuitem></menuchoice> eest."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Putting"
msgstr "Täiustatud puttamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Advanced putting can be enabled by checking "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Enable Advanced "
#| "Putting</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This putting mode is slightly more "
#| "challenging than the regular click-and-hold mode, and can be used with "
#| "either the mouse or keyboard."
msgid ""
"Advanced putting can be enabled by checking the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Enable Advanced "
"Putting</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. This putting mode is slightly "
"more challenging than the regular click-and-hold mode, and can be used with "
"either the mouse or keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Täiustatud puttamise saab lubada menüükäsu <menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Täiustatud puttamine lubatud</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"märkimisega. See režiim on omajagu keerukam kui tavaline klõpsa-ja-hoia "
"meetod ning sedagi on võimalik kasutada nii hiire kui klaviatuuriga."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "To putt in this mode:"
msgstr "Selles režiimis puttamiseks:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Click or press the <keycap>Down Arrow</keycap> key once to begin the "
#| "swing. The putting indicator will appear, and the strength gauge will "
#| "start filling up with a color, which changes as the gauge fills up."
msgid ""
"Click or press the &Down; arrow key once to begin the swing. The putting "
"indicator will appear, and the strength gauge will start filling up with a "
"color, which changes as the gauge fills up."
msgstr ""
"Klõpsa või vajuta klahvi <keycap>Nool alla</keycap> löögi alustamiseks. "
"Ilmub indikaator ning löögitugevuse rõngas hakkab täituma värviga."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Click or press the <keycap>Down Arrow</keycap> key when the strength "
#| "gauge has filled up the amount that you want. The farther around the "
#| "circle the strength gauge has filled up, the stronger the putt will be. "
#| "It takes practice to be able to get the correct strength on putts."
msgid ""
"Click or press the &Down; arrow key when the strength gauge has filled up "
"the amount that you want. The farther around the circle the strength gauge "
"has filled up, the stronger the putt will be. It takes practice to be able "
"to get the correct strength on putts."
msgstr ""
"Klõpsa või vajuta klahvi <keycap>Nool alla</keycap>, kui löögitugevus on "
"rõngal jõudnud tasemeni, mida soovid. Mida enam rõngas on täitunud, seda "
"tugevam löök tuleb. Õige löögitugevuse tunde leidmiseks kulub päris hulk "
"aega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After this, the color in the putting indicator will start to wind down back "
"to where it started."
msgstr "Seejärel hakkab värv indikaatorirõngas taas kahanema alguse poole."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Click or press the <keycap>Down Arrow</keycap> key again when the "
#| "strength-indicator is as close as possible to the center line of the "
#| "putting indicator."
msgid ""
"Click or press the &Down; arrow key again when the strength-indicator is as "
"close as possible to the center line of the putting indicator."
msgstr ""
"Klõpsa või vajuta klahvi <keycap>Nool alla</keycap> uuesti, kui "
"tugevusindikaator on võimalikult lähedal puttamisindikaatori keskjoonele."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The closer the final click (or key press) is, the more true the putt is to "
"the original line."
msgstr ""
"Mida lähemal viimane klõps (või klahvivajutus) on, seda täpsemalt kulgeb "
"löök esialgu määratud suunas."

